		<p>Product designer and front-end engineer based in Brooklyn, New York. I’ve had the privilege of working with many talented folks at <a class="intro-apple" target="_blank" href="http://www.apple.com/">Apple</a>, <a class="intro-cover" target="_blank"  href="http://www.paywithcover.com/">Cover</a>, <a class="intro-space" target="_blank" href="http://www.space150.com/">space150</a>, <a class="intro-nerdery" href="https://nerdery.com/">The Nerdery</a>, and more. Sometimes I work on side projects like <a class="intro-wallpaper-disco" target="_blank" href="http://wallpaperdisco.com/">Wallpaper Disco</a> and <a class="intro-bullshit-sheriff" taget="_blank" href="http://bullshitsheriff.com/">Bullshit Sheriff</a>. I make a mean Manhattan and skateboard like a boss. Let's grab a coffee sometime.</p>
